        <div xml:id="AN10-kilavi"></div>
        <div xml:id="AN10">
            <lg type="edition"><l>vāṉkaṭ parappiṟ ṟūvaṟ ketiriya</l>
<l>mīṉkaṇ ṭaṉṉa mellarum pūḻtta</l>
<l>muṭavumutir puṉṉait taṭavunilai mācciṉaip</l>
<l>puḷḷiṟai kūru mellam pulampa</l>
<l>neyta luṇkaṇ <choice><seg>paita</seg><seg>paitala</seg></choice> <choice><seg>luḻappap</seg><seg>kaluḻap</seg></choice></l>
<l>pirita leṇṇiṉai <choice><seg>yāyi</seg><seg>yāyiṉ</seg></choice> ṉaṉṟu</l>
<l>marituṟ ṟaṉaiyāṟ peruma <choice><seg>vuritaṉiṟ</seg><seg>vu<supplied>ri</supplied>tiṉiṟ</seg></choice></l>
<l>koṇṭāṅkup peyartal vēṇṭuṅ koṇṭaloṭu</l>
<l><choice><seg>kuḻūukki<supplied>ḷai</supplied>p</seg><seg>kuḻūuttiraip</seg></choice> puṇari <choice><seg>yaṭaitaru</seg><seg>yuṭaitaru</seg></choice> mekkarp</l>
<l>paḻantimil <choice><seg>ceṉṟa</seg><seg>koṉṟa</seg></choice> putuvalaip paratavar</l>
<l>mōṭṭumaṇa laṭaikaraik kōṭṭumīṉ koṇṭi</l>
<l>maṇaṅkamaḻ pākkattup pakukkum</l>
<l>vaḷaṅkeḻu toṇṭi yaṉṉaviva ṇalaṉē.</l></lg>
            <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O soft man from the lonely [seashore], where birds abound on seats</l>
<l rend="indent">	in the broad-standing big branches of the <choice><seg>bent-over </seg><seg>limping(?) </seg></choice> aging mastwood tree</l>
<l rend="indent">	on which soft buds have withered that look like stars,</l>
<l rend="indent">	exposed to the spray, in the expanse of the sky area,</l>
<l>when you considered separating,</l>
<l rend="indent">	so that [her] water-lily collyrium eyes <choice><seg>bear </seg><seg>dim </seg></choice> <choice><seg>sorrow,</seg><seg>sorrowfully,</seg></choice> </l>
<l>you took to something very difficult indeed.</l>
<l>It is necessary to return there, bringing [it back] as is right,</l>
<l>– her goodness, like wealthy Toṇṭi,</l>
<l rend="indent">	where the fishermen with new nets, who had <choice><seg>gone in </seg><seg>killed from </seg></choice> [their] old boats</l>
<l><choice><seg>	through </seg><seg>	by the </seg></choice> dunes, where <choice><seg>waves, with relations in a crowd, approach with </seg><seg>the ocean breaks with crowding waves, in </seg></choice> the east wind,</l>
<l rend="indent">	distribute the pillage of swordfish on the shore set with high sand</l>
<l><choice><seg>	by </seg><seg>	in </seg></choice> the villages fragrant with scent.</l>
<l>7+13	you were in great difficulty indeed<note place="foot">Perhaps here too it is possible to connect the nalaṉ, even easier since there is no dative mark.</note></l>
<l rend="indent">	because of the beauty of her…</l></lg>
        </div>
    </body>
